DataElement.preferredName: Diagnostic Computed Tomography Performed Month Number
DataElement.preferredDefinition: Numeric value that represents the month that a diagnostic computed tomography scan was performed.

DataElementConcept.preferredDefinition: information related to a diagnostic computed tomography scan performed.
